      <p class="hero-sub">
        Expert tree care for homeowners and businesses across Forney, Crandall, Kemp, 
        Waxahachie, and the greater DFW area. Licensed, insured, and always committed 
        to doing the job right.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="font-size:16px; padding:16px 32px;">
          Get a Free Estimate →
        </a>
        <a href="tel:4694372740" class="btn-outline" style="font-size:16px; padding:15px 32px;">
          📞 469-437-2740
